snippet.title: Toontown: Corporate Clash - Hires & Heroes (v1.3.0) Trailer
snippet.description:
The Hires & Heroes Update releases soon! Check out the Gameplay Trailer, which includes over 4 minutes of new footage and information, including the release date!

Main Video Editor: Rox
Additional Video Editors: Alex the Wizard, Main, Snoopee
Footage Gatherer: Trip 
Script: Alex the Wizard, Duke Trickyflip, Rox
Music: Duke Trickyflip
Hires & Heroes Logo: Aero
Hires & Heroes Logo Animation: Rox
Main Logo Animation: Toonsies


▼  Connect with us:
Join our Team: https://corporateclash.net/apply
Website: https://corporateclash.net
Discord: https://corporateclash.net/social/discord
Twitter: https://corporateclash.net/social/twitter

▼ What is Toontown?

Toontown: Corporate Clash is a completely free-to-play massively multiplayer online game designed to be a reimagined experience of Disney's Toontown Online. Suitable for players of all ages, ANYONE can have fun joining in the battle against the evil robot "Cogs". Create a new Toon, grab a few Gags and dive right into the never-ending battle to save Toontown from the Cogs! What are you waiting for?

--

Disclaimer:

Toontown: Corporate Clash is a completely free-to-play independent project funded solely by the team. No revenue of any sort is generated through this game. In no way, form, or shape is Toontown: Corporate Clash connected to or affiliated with The Walt Disney Company and/or the Disney Interactive Media Group.
